origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "BankCompliance.get_regulatory_warnings",
        "description": "获取指定时间段内的监管警告信息",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "time_period",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "指定的时间段，格式为YYYY-MM-DD至YYYY-MM-DD"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "warning_count",
                "description": "返回的警告数量"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "BankCompliance.analyze_communication_issues",
        "description": "分析通信数据中的合规问题",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "communication_data",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "需要分析的通信数据"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "issues_and_feedback",
                "description": "分析结果，包括问题和反馈"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "BankCompliance.get_communication_data",
        "description": "获取指定时间段内的通信数据",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "time_period",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "指定的时间段，格式为YYYY-MM-DD至YYYY-MM-DD"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "communication_data",
                "description": "返回的通信数据"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "BankCompliance.provide_improvement_suggestions",
        "description": "根据通信数据、问题反馈和警告数量提供改进建议",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "communication_data",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "通信数据"
            },
            {
                "name": "issues_and_feedback",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "问题和反馈"
            },
            {
                "name": "warning_count",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "警告数量"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "improvement_suggestions",
                "description": "改进建议"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "BankCompliance.monitor_transaction_patterns",
        "description": "监控交易模式以识别潜在的合规风险",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "transaction_data",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "交易数据"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "risk_indicators",
                "description": "风险指标"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "BankCompliance.audit_customer_interactions",
        "description": "审计客户交互记录以确保合规性",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "interaction_data",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "客户交互数据"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "compliance_status",
                "description": "合规状态"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "BankCompliance.generate_compliance_report",
        "description": "生成合规报告",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "report_period",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "报告的时间段，格式为YYYY-MM-DD至YYYY-MM-DD"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "compliance_report",
                "description": "合规报告"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "BankCompliance.track_regulatory_changes",
        "description": "跟踪监管变化并提供更新信息",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "update_frequency",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "更新频率，如每日、每周、每月"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "regulatory_updates",
                "description": "监管更新信息"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "BankCompliance.evaluate_risk_profile",
        "description": "评估客户的风险概况",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "customer_data",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "客户数据"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "risk_profile",
                "description": "风险概况"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
